of toast, huh?

49:07.303 --> 49:09.095
No, just like I didn't
begrudge you

49:09.095 --> 49:11.303
the ten grand
you lost gambling.

49:11.303 --> 49:12.637
-Oh.
-[Cathy] "Oh". "Oh"?

49:12.637 --> 49:14.595
Yeah, look at me right now.

49:14.595 --> 49:16.595
You are not getting another
fucking dime of that money.

49:16.595 --> 49:18.679
-You understand me?
-Is that why you think I'm here?

49:18.679 --> 49:19.887
You think I'm haunting you
for money?

49:19.887 --> 49:21.595
-I didn't say that.
-Yeah? Well--

49:21.595 --> 49:23.095
There's a lot going on, Jimmy.

49:23.095 --> 49:25.303
And what the fuck
did I do?

49:25.303 --> 49:26.887
Nothing.

49:26.887 --> 49:28.261
But you tend to remind people
of things

49:28.261 --> 49:30.136
-they don't need reminding of.
-Like who?

49:33.136 --> 49:34.679
Kick? Did she say that?

49:34.679 --> 49:36.679
[Cathy] Oh, what, is shock you,
you bother people?

49:36.679 --> 49:38.261
-Fuck you, Cathy.
-[Frankie] Hey.

49:39.512 --> 49:42.553
Tommy got questioned

49:42.553 --> 49:44.261
about Kinicki.

49:44.261 --> 49:46.428
All right? People are looking
into what happened.

49:48.929 --> 49:50.762
Did Tommy get subpoenaed?

49:50.762 --> 49:51.970
[Cathy]
He expects to be.

49:53.804 --> 49:56.261
Does Tommy have a lawyer?

49:56.261 --> 49:58.345
How the fuck could he
afford that, huh?

50:02.720 --> 50:05.095
So you gave him the money?

50:05.095 --> 50:07.178
You gave Tommy
the fucking money?

50:07.178 --> 50:09.178
[Cathy] Oh, hey, Tommy doesn't
cause his fucking problems.

50:09.178 --> 50:11.053
[Jimmy]
Fuck you! Fuck you both, huh.

50:11.053 --> 50:13.345
[Cathy]
Yeah, get the fuck out of here.

50:15.303 --> 50:17.220
Fuck it. Fuck it.

50:17.220 --> 50:18.595
[sighs]

50:18.595 --> 50:20.512
[muttering]

50:20.512 --> 50:21.929
Fuck!

