checked out.

51:41.470 --> 51:43.887
Now, where the fuck
is the armored car, Jimmy?

51:43.887 --> 51:45.679
Clay Marsh,
near the bait shop.

51:45.679 --> 51:46.970
Hmm.

51:52.136 --> 51:54.637
Hey, what's the most you ever
lost on a bet?

51:54.637 --> 51:56.387
That's easy. Hagler.

51:56.387 --> 51:58.136
Yeah?

51:58.136 --> 51:59.887
I guess everyone lost
on that fucking fight, huh?

51:59.887 --> 52:01.303
-Yeah. You too?
-Yup.

52:01.303 --> 52:03.762
Marvelous Marvin Hagler.

52:03.762 --> 52:05.553
Did everything he could,
but the fix was in.

52:05.553 --> 52:07.804
There was nothing he could do.
Beat Leonard's brains in

52:07.804 --> 52:09.470
and he still lost
the fucking fight.

52:09.470 --> 52:13.095
Hey, let that be
your worst loss, Jimmy.

52:13.095 --> 52:14.512
There's only, like,
18 grand here.

52:14.512 --> 52:16.053
